derstand the technical side of the Apto platform and be able to speak to customers' product and engineering teams. Be able to present technical information about Apto services and conduct product demonstrations if needed. Serve as the link between the Operations and Engineering teams. Have relevant knowledge in financial services, preferably payments, and specifically in transaction processing. Communicate with clarity and charisma. Explain technical concepts in a digestible manner. Be excited about to customer-facing responsibilities Explain technical solutions to a diverse audience using appropriate language. Skills: Knack for customer service and high levels of satisfaction. Excellent communication skills. Proven ability to manage goals and deadlines effectively. Passion for learning. Benefits: Competitive salary and equity Fully paid healthcare for you and dependants Great team of driven people with different skill sets Flexible hours and work from home days (fully remote during COVID-19) Opportunity to build solutions for millions of people around the world aIBpQFEJb4 ", 
